description:
On July 4, Americans celebrate freedom. But are they really free? Due to Covid-19, millions dont feel free at all. Racism still plagues humanity, plus countless other problems. In his July 4, 2020 message, Pastor Steve Wohlberg reveals where true freedom can be found.
